  "text": "The contribution points of this paper can be summarized as: [CITATION_1] . We consider the current device for recommending the TV programs that device can display [CITATION_2] . Finding the KNN users using combination of similarity and social value of the user (3). Improve the users' similarity by incorporating the Pearson Correlation Coefficient, Evaluated resources and direct trust in the form of opinions and comments.",
